title: Panic outside White House after shots fired
text:
Panic outside White House after shots fired 2:06pm EST - 00:38 
People run from the north fence line of the White House after an unidentified adult man was wounded outside, in what police said was being investigated as a self-inflicted shooting. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
